{"tid":1993633,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"二橋重開 院長舉勝利手勢","createTime":"2020-04-29T01:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T15:04:12.000Z","uid":228441,"like":3,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f12e02c416b78779eb89347bcbc2a205cda21d07","tid":1993633,"uid":228441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T01:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPyL1xc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPyL1xc.png&h=6c32be82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vV8PJLy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvV8PJLy.jpg&h=86c6d498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呀院長 你d學生個晚差d畀人殺晒<br />\n有咩咁值得慶祝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de70cb0e0c6d5a89686bd2456463571bac8bffb0","tid":1993633,"uid":264245,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"雖然個手勢都可以硬解成二號...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cebd8a6a9ba03b2c78e6dd3b49ed0c871432c21","tid":1993633,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T01:56:33.000Z","msg":"終於都露底了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403a870010793e8939280cfc63c4928a7ffe01bd","tid":1993633,"uid":258598,"like":4,"dislike":50,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91a73de61aab5a186b04d1374430d958f99382fa","tid":1993633,"uid":228441,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"403a870010793e8939280cfc63c4928a7ffe01bd","tid":1993633,"uid":258598,"like":4,"dislike":50,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:00:04.000Z","msg":"平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e620b578b97ca67ed51eeee542be51dea00351f","tid":1993633,"uid":258731,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"【打柒支那01】共派政黨民建聯得分上升8% 黨媒01是背後元兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1993353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1993353</a><br />\n<br />\n支那01帶風向同滲透已經延伸到連登外面 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家訓醒未</span></span><br />\n立法會選戰 連登仔第一個考驗：打柒支那01<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LD7dnxE.png\" /><br />\n知唔知道點解今次中共病毒疫情，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共派政黨</span></span></strong>，特別係<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯</span>，民意得分直線上升???<br />\n答案：係因為支那01係背後緊搞鬼！！<br />\n『<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fchi%2Fpress-release%2F2020%2F20200428-chi&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=349a9bcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi</a><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">公民黨的評分較七個月前顯著下跌5.7分，是其於2006年上榜以來的新低，</span></em>而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯則顯著上升8.4分。</span></span>』<br />\n<br />\n2020.04.24 損人不利己並非為政之道<br />\nWHAT THE FUCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刻意放大公民黨郭榮鏗 「阻住晒」「影響民生，議會運作」的負面形象<br />\n堅守議會 減慢赤化速度 阻止23條立法絕口不提<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200425/330694038183350272.jpeg/xOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200425%2F330694038183350272.jpeg%2FxOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=6337beae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news，唔好再被佢帶風向<br />\n搞鳩我哋香港人咁撚耐 支那01呢條數香港人未同你計 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年反送中大家唔係未領教過 唔記得嘅幫你重溫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那01滲透連登亂鳩咁帶風向 搞到我哋抗爭路途艱難咗咁多 你唔係唔記得呀嘛？<br />\n2019.10.06 曲解個別人士看法 為連登仔「主流」意見<br />\n不排除發表裝修過火言論人士係01自己友裡應外合 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3372054/org/275d81f556563cc11f7f4df5bd1b3a68.jpg/ZNGnljnlcF3bfZKzYGOuq1MS4Xzj4awRMtY9gTLWPYE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3372054%2Forg%2F275d81f556563cc11f7f4df5bd1b3a68.jpg%2FZNGnljnlcF3bfZKzYGOuq1MS4Xzj4awRMtY9gTLWPYE%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=7861ddf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019.09.22 試圖用煽情手段令人對示威者反感<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317339/org/21f8e8c12ac3ac88cdc4ad6d7d99f723.jpg/AT1fGhI0UWexOIYV9dBE_Of_yZ-j--bEbklny25JZ8s?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317339%2Forg%2F21f8e8c12ac3ac88cdc4ad6d7d99f723.jpg%2FAT1fGhI0UWexOIYV9dBE_Of_yZ-j--bEbklny25JZ8s%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=6fda6241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那01最近已經現撚晒形，直頭唔同你扮<br />\n2020.04.27 合理化中聯辦港澳辦在港干預內部事務 爭取政治話語權行為<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200427/331515838307897345.jpeg/xDRqAvnvB84AtlSIOBccWOQrCm3_BnxUKz52rSs-dq0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200427%2F331515838307897345.jpeg%2FxDRqAvnvB84AtlSIOBccWOQrCm3_BnxUKz52rSs-dq0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bdd570dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020.04.25 口罩問題拖慢嚟處理 港共遲遲唔封關 要手足炸羅湖關口 醫護罷工先肯「局部封鎖」，如果咁樣都唔慢點樣先算慢？？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200425/330700382865068033.jpeg/dVvhHBAxURJ0q55foYVsUOigJsUP_8ZdPbyKZz28imc?v=w480r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200425%2F330700382865068033.jpeg%2FdVvhHBAxURJ0q55foYVsUOigJsUP_8ZdPbyKZz28imc%3Fv%3Dw480r16_9&h=ee7057e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近搭車，仲係見到好多港豬攞住手機睇01，此風不可長！！！<br />\n支那01最近仲成為咗網上媒體market share第一，01笑緊你哋班港豬同連燈仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4384168/org/8c15ee579b80fc401ab1007b7e6688a1.jpg/RBgNUKrwXNjia4szpNiqu7ZA6PHA5gHvAEV_ugBFf7o?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4384168%2Forg%2F8c15ee579b80fc401ab1007b7e6688a1.jpg%2FRBgNUKrwXNjia4szpNiqu7ZA6PHA5gHvAEV_ugBFf7o%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=aad31c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle新聞News Feed，如果見到01啲新聞彈出嚟，記得取消追蹤！<br />\n自己做完之後，記得幫自己屋企人做，做完之後幫朋友做<br />\n一傳十，十傳百，發揮群眾力量<br />\n一定要打撚柒支那01<br />\n<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news<br />\n因為好重要 所以要講三次<br />\n<br />\n支那01，一定要打撚柒佢<br />\n守護香港，反對紅媒滲透<br />\ntelegram group: <a href=\"http://t.me/fuckyougna01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffuckyougna01&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=9643914f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/fuckyougna01</a><br />\ntelegram channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/fuckyouchina01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffuckyouchina01&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=5a9ea04e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fuckyouchina01</a>"},{"pid":"8597b77e21b964c0f17983b2eaa61a57f35fc48d","tid":1993633,"uid":442,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"403a870010793e8939280cfc63c4928a7ffe01bd","tid":1993633,"uid":258598,"like":4,"dislike":50,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"個晚所有人都以為中大既人會死"},{"pid":"304d210fe5045cf21f3d947a0f4bfdb626c61bfa","tid":1993633,"uid":258598,"like":4,"dislike":32,"score":-28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e4eac519c0abf66a308d3d045d5d8ea6aea3564","tid":1993633,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"304d210fe5045cf21f3d947a0f4bfdb626c61bfa","tid":1993633,"uid":258598,"like":4,"